column5: Was at Miles Bay July 31-Aug. 9. Cold, wet and windy most of the week. Found a few walleye but not like usual. Here's a pic of me and my dog admiring a muskie my wife caught. Back up in seven weeks for the fall bite.https://www.walleyecentral.com/forums...pictureid=2737
I fish the same area and I noticed in your photo album you fishing the jugs. Do you stay at Grassy?
Congrats to the wife Nice fish!
Yes, been going to Grassy twice a year since 1999. Will you be there this fall? We'll be back Oct. 2-11.
We will be there 2nd week in September. We also go the 2nd week of June.
